": {\r\n        "fr": "Instagram",\r\n        "en": "Instagram"\r\n      }\r\n    },\r\n    {\r\n      "name": "dailymotionurl",\r\n      "type": "public",\r\n      "fieldType": "url",\r\n      "optional": true,\r\n      "max": 300,\r\n      "label": {\r\n        "fr": "Dailymotion",\r\n        "en": "Dailymotion"\r\n      }\r\n    },\r\n    {\r\n      "name": "youtubeurl",\r\n      "type": "public",\r\n      "fieldType": "url",\r\n      "optional": true,\r\n      "max": 300,\r\n      "label": {\r\n        "fr": "Youtube",\r\n        "en": "Youtube"\r\n      }\r\n    },\r\n    {\r\n      "name": "linkedinurl",\r\n      "type": "public",\r\n      "fieldType": "url",\r\n      "optional": true,\r\n      "max": 300,\r\n      "label": {\r\n        "fr": "LinkedIn",\r\n        "en": "LinkedIn"\r\n      }\r\n    },\r\n    {\r\n      "name": "testimony",\r\n      "type": "public",\r\n      "fieldType": "textarea",\r\n      "optional": true,\r\n      "multilingual": true,\r\n      "label": {\r\n        "fr": "Témoignage",\r\n        "en": "Testimony"\r\n      },\r\n      "info": {\r\n        "fr": "Merci d''ajouter du texte et non des liens!",\r\n        "en": "Thank you for adding text rather than links!"\r\n      }\r\n    },\r\n    {\r\n      "name": "imagetestimony",\r\n      "type": "public",\r\n      "fieldType": "text",\r\n      "optional": true,\r\n      "label": {\r\n        "fr": "Url image témoignages",\r\n        "en": "Url of image of testimonies"\r\n      }\r\n    },\r\n    {\r\n      "name": "authortestimony",\r\n      "type": "public",\r\n      "fieldType": "text",\r\n      "optional": true,\r\n      "label": {\r\n        "fr": "Auteur du témoignage",\r\n        "en": "Author of the testimony"\r\n      }\r\n    },\r\n    {\r\n      "name": "illustrationurl",\r\n      "type": "public",\r\n      "fieldType": "url",\r\n      "optional": true,\r\n      "info": {\r\n        "fr": "Collez un lien pointant vers l''illustration",\r\n        "en": "Paste an url pointing to the illustration"\r\n      },\r\n      "label": {\r\n        "fr": "Photo d''illustration",\r\n        "en": "Illustration photo"\r\n      }\r\n    },\r\n    {\r\n      "name": "illustration",\r\n      "fieldType": "image",\r\n      "type": "public",\r\n      "optional": true,\r\n      "label": {\r\n        "fr": "Photo d''illustration",\r\n        "en": "Partner illustration"\r\n      },\r\n      "info": {\r\n        "fr": "Chargez l''illustration utilisée sur le champ précédent",\r\n        "en": "Load the image used in the previous field"\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n  ],\r\n  "dataviz": "[{\\"sections\\":[\\"year\\"]}]"\r\n}', 2, 'IMPORTANT : les logos ne doivent pas dépasser 1 Mo, et doivent faire minimum 500 pixels de largeur.\r\nLes salons ont tous été créés, il suffit de faire des mises à jour (de logos, de chiffres, de textes) et de dupliquer pour les prochaines éditions, même sans connaître les dates (renseignez le 1er du mois).\r\nPour la création d''un nouvel événement, merci de contacter la direction de la communication au préalable.\r\nDans le champ "témoignages", seul du texte est autorisé (pas de lien url), ne pas mettre les guillemets de la citation. Ils apparaîtront automatiquement sur le site. \r\nPour toute question, la direction de la communication reste à votre disposition. \r\n \r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL),
