(4419, 'On the road to COP21 ', 6413, 'placetob', 'Calendar of COP21 events in Paris and Beyond', 'review_agenda-place-to-b_00.jpg', 'http://www.placetob.org/', 0, '2015-10-23 15:26:49', '2016-09-30 16:17:13', 27004436, 0, '{"order":"relative","dataviz":"[{\\"sections\\":[\\"tag\\"],\\"filter\\":\\"upcoming\\"}]","moderated":false,"send_invitation_email":true,"contributorconfigstep":-1,"cFields":{"organization":[],"contact_name":[]}}', 1, 'Hello,\r\n\r\nYou are about to propose an event in the collaborative agenda of Place to B. Thanks! This agenda aims to identify clearly and succinctly a wide range of events around the COP21 in Paris and beyond.\r\nBefore you begin: Verify that the event you want to add is not already in our database, using the search engine!\r\n\r\nPlease, don''t miss to fill in all the fields provided and be as specific as possible in your descriptions to make your audience want to participate. Remember to upload an image and provide a link to your website (if you have one). Please use the tags that are offered. We remind you that it is also good to indicate a contact for any questions about your event. And above all, please take the time to proofread before publishing your contribution! We urge you to provide bilingual content (French and English) by clicking on "Add a language".\r\n\r\nOur team will validate this contribution within 48 hours. For more information, thank you to refer to OpenAgenda''s help page.\r\n\r\nPlace to B thanks you to commit yourself for spreading a new voice of change during the COP21 in Paris!', NULL, NULL, NULL),
